text: Olshany (, ) is a town in Republic of Belarus, located in Stolin District, Brest Region. Its documental records began in 1392. ==History== In 2009, the town of Olshany became an agrotown.Stolin Region News, April 2004. ==External links== * Olshany at Radzima.org * Olshany at tut.by ==References== Category:Towns in Belarus Category:Populated places in Brest Region Category:Stolin District
